Nootka 0.7.7 beta 1
===========================
===========BUILD===========
===========================

Requirements:
- Qt libraries (obviously)
- Portaudio
    For Windows Portaudio have to be compiled with directsound or ASIO
    (see Portaudio build instructions)
- libasound-dev under linux


- Unpack tarball
- create some dir (f. e. "build") out of unpacked source directory
- go to build dir
- cmake ../nootka-0.7.7 (or ccmake or qtcmake with GUI)
  select PORTAUDIO_LIBRARIES variable if Your PA is somewhere else than usualy
- make
- make install (usually as root)

to remove (uninstall)
- make uninstall (usually as root)



